## How to Use Slash Commands

### In Cursor Chat
1. Type `/` in the chat input to see available commands
2. Select a command or type the full command name
3. Add your query or context after the command
4. The command will apply the appropriate prompt template from mcp-prompts

### Command Format
```
/command [your query or context]
```

### Examples
```
/analysis What are the memory usage patterns in src/main.cpp?

/architecture Design a message passing system for ESP32 to Android communication

/conan How should I configure Conan profiles for multi-target deployment?

/refactoring Refactor bpm_detector.h to use smart pointers and RAII
```

