## MCP Server Configuration

The mcp-prompts server is configured in `.claude/mcp.json`:
```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "prompts": {
      "command": "mcp-prompts",
      "args": ["--storage", "file", "--path", "/home/sparrow/projects/ai-mcp-monorepo/packages/mcp-prompts/data/prompts"]
    }
  }
}
```

